export const querys = {
    obtenerTodosProductos: "SELECT TOP(500) * FROM [webstore].[dbo].[Products]",
    obtenerProductoById: "SELECT * FROM Products Where Id = @Id",
    registrarProducto:
      "INSERT INTO [webstore].[dbo].[Products] (name, description, quantity) VALUES (@name,@description,@quantity);",
    eliminarProducto: "DELETE FROM [webstore].[dbo].[Products] WHERE Id= @Id",
    obtenerTotalProductos: "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM webstore.dbo.Products",
    ActualizarProductoById:
      "UPDATE [webstore].[dbo].[Products] SET Name = @name, Description = @description, Quantity = @quantity WHERE Id = @id",
    obtenerTodosClientes : "SELECT * FROM Cliente",
  };
